At the Oteybis perimeter defense all the troops begin to hear aloud 
whistling noise, one that seemingly grows louder and louder still. 
Suddenly the two Infecticon ships that launched before speed past the 
perimeter defense heading towards the Oteybis.(Sorry if I spelled it 
wrong.) On the ground beneath where the ships passed the defense lies 
two silver discs that werent there before, Each one reads "25 cents".
